006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model;
007
008import java.util.List;
009import java.util.Map;
010
011import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
012
013public interface IFeatureContainerModelAssembly<
014    MI extends IModelInstanceAbsolute,
015    NMI extends INamedModelInstanceAbsolute,
016    FI extends IFieldInstanceAbsolute,
017    AI extends IAssemblyInstanceAbsolute,
018    CI extends IChoiceInstance,
019    CGI extends IChoiceGroupInstance>
020    extends IContainerModelAssembly,
021    IFeatureContainerModelAbsolute<MI, NMI, FI, AI> {
022  /**
023   * Get the model container implementation instance.
024   *
025   * @return the model container instance
026   */
027  @Override
028  @NonNull
029  IContainerModelAssemblySupport<MI, NMI, FI, AI, CI, CGI> getModelContainer();
030
031  @Override
032  default List<CI> getChoiceInstances() {
033    return getModelContainer().getChoiceInstances();
034  }
035
036  @Override
037  default CGI getChoiceGroupInstanceByName(String name) {
038    return getModelContainer().getChoiceGroupInstanceMap().get(name);
039  }
040
041  @Override
042  default Map<String, CGI> getChoiceGroupInstances() {
043    return getModelContainer().getChoiceGroupInstanceMap();
044  }
045}
